{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204910/extras/add-slipgate-to-your-wishlist-and-subscribe-eng.gif?t=1737487276\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204910/extras/logo_transparent.png?t=1737487276\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MEAT SCI-FI RETRO SHOOTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Slipgate</strong> is a classic retro shooter that leads you into brutal battles in the corridors of a military base overrun by demons. Become <strong>Jack &quot;Hammer&quot; Thompso</strong>n, a fearless Marine who never backs down from danger. Get back into action, save your wife and stop the end of the world from coming. You have to go through mysterious laboratories, outposts of a destroyed world and ancient temples, fight demons and giants.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GRAB YOUR FAVORITE WEAPON AND LET THE INFERNAL CREATURES FALL! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204910/extras/gameplay-classicheskogo-retro-shutera-slipgate.gif?t=1737487276\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TRUE TO ROOTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We use the 15 year old FPS Creator engine, with improved graphics and powerful gameplay. This allows the game to inherit the DNA of such masterpieces as Doom, Quake, Half-Life and SiN. <strong><i>This is a childhood game... made now.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204910/extras/retro-igra-i-retro-tehnologii-slipgate.gif?t=1737487276\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">THE STORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Humanity has made a grave mistake. The gates of Hell are open again and the demons are here. Only one man stands between Hell and Earth, and that man is you. And more than that, somewhere on the other side of the hellish portal, your wife is waiting for salvation. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>You have a long way to go, in fountains of blood and shells, knee-deep in blood, one touch with death. Feeding on the power of demons, go through other worlds and unravel all the mysteries of the teleportation complex... </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>But are you sure that true Evil is on the other side of the gate?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204910/extras/sm2.jpg?t=1737487276\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The atmosphere of <strong>cold horror </strong>and loneliness, broken only by fierce battles with demons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The body of your hero is <strong>too human</strong>, and one blow of the clawed paw can be fatal. Feed on the power of your enemies to become more powerful!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each opponent requires a different approach. They don't just push through - they have <strong>a tactic</strong>, and they stick to it.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are confronted not by faceless evil, but by the enterprising and <strong>active general of Hell</strong>. Don't think this walk would be easy!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Look for runes to unlock new possibilities. Move around the battlefield with a grappling hook, freeze enemies, destroy their shields, improvise!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A wide arsenal of tools of destruction, from the usual shotguns and chainguns, to exotics like the dematerializer and reducer.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204910/extras/base2.jpg?t=1737487276\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204910/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737487276","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204910/page.bg.jpg?t=1737487276","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204910/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737487276","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204910/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737487276","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"Blood and gore, violence."},"demos":[{"appid":2640350,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204910/extras/add-slipgate-to-your-wishlist-and-subscribe-eng.gif?t=1737487276\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204910/extras/logo_transparent.png?t=1737487276\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MEAT SCI-FI RETRO SHOOTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Slipgate</strong> is a classic retro shooter that leads you into brutal battles in the corridors of a military base overrun by demons. Become <strong>Jack &quot;Hammer&quot; Thompso</strong>n, a fearless Marine who never backs down from danger. Get back into action, save your wife and stop the end of the world from coming. You have to go through mysterious laboratories, outposts of a destroyed world and ancient temples, fight demons and giants.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GRAB YOUR FAVORITE WEAPON AND LET THE INFERNAL CREATURES FALL! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item